data.description: A rare find!!!! Main house + guest house + detached garage that holds an RV! John Houston built home with a flexible floor plan.  Main house has 3 bedrooms + an office or 4 bedrooms-you decide! Spacious living area with open concept kitchen & dining. Gorgeous copper sink in kitchen. Split bedroom arrangement. Master suite is spacious, master bath has split vanities, separate tub & shower--nice walk in closet.  Secondary living room or bonus room is upstairs. Good closet space throughout. FABULOUS back porch with vaulted ceiling & wood details! Relax on the porch & cook out, too.  Tons of concrete. Detached garage holds Sprinter RV and has a workshop area, or small garage space for a motorcycle, ATV, or a small car. Steps away from the main house is a detached guest house that is one bedroom & one bath (with handicap shower) that is fully equipped with appliances. Guest house has separate septic. Fenced back yard. Move in ready! No HOA, county taxes, Midlothian Heritage school zone.
